      "rationale": "Validation was performed on the FDA generic centrifugal pump, which shares the same centrifugal topology and operating regime (flow rates 2.5–7 L/min, rotational speeds 2000–3500 RPM) as the COU device. The validation domain spans the full COU operating space."
    },
