    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The 6 not-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3. CFD predictions of hemolysis index agree with FDA benchmark experimental data within combined uncertainty bands across all 5 operating points. The relative hemolysis index RH < 1 criterion is satisfied, supporting the conclusion that the model can reliably identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
